<center>
<h3 align="center" style="margin-bottom: 0pt;"><i>The Center for Human
Modeling and Simulation:</i> </h3>
</center>
<p> The overall goals of the Center for Human Modeling and Simulation
are the investigation of computer graphics modeling and animation
techniques, especially for synthetic humans. The HMS Center originated
the <i>Jack </i>software. Major focii are in real-time,
behavior-based animation of human movement and understanding the
relationship between human movement, natural language, instructions and
communication. </p>
